name: Teleprompter EP
description:
The awesome new release from Brisbane based Teleprompter. Recorded at Gasworks studios, and produced by Yama Indra of Gloves/Damn Arms fame. Featuring 4 new tracks and a remix of old an old favourite by an international artist, you'll want to get your mitts on this ASAP.

Track Listing

1. Dinobot
2. Banshee
3. Lung-Tied
4. Lambda
5. Boxcutter (R3 Remix)

Free personal delivery for those in Brisbane (within reason). Or postage anywhere else for not much more!

EXCITEMENT!
